po-and-aogiri-high-school-management-companies-collaborate-on-anti-slander-measures/">布斯波！・青桐高中双方管理公司合作防止诽谤</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Buspo！青桐高中的两家管理公司合作防止诽谤” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/both-vspo-and-aogiri-high-school-management-companies-collaborate-on-anti-slander-measures/embed/#?secret=yjcD1rzmlf#?secret=NLxoVapM40" data-secret="NLxoVapM40" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://aogirihighschool.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">青桐高中</a></p><cite>维维昂有限公司</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-aogiri-high-school-official-youtube-channel-reached-900k-subscribers/">VTuber 后组青桐高中 YouTube 官方频道订阅人数达 90 万，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-aogiri-high-school-official-youtube-channel-reached-900k-subscribers/feed/ 0 111423
